        "zh": "1.就業市場與人力任用 <br>2.勞動法規與工作分析<br>3.人才招募策略<br>4.求職者篩選技巧 <br>5.甄選測量與決策 <br>6.甄選工具<br>7.面談技巧<br>",
        "en": "1. Employment market and personnel staffing<br>2. Labor laws and job analysis<br>3. Talented person recruiting strategy<br>4. Job applicant screening tips<br>5. Selection measurement and decision<br>6. Selection tools<br>7. Interview skills<br>"
